stem cell test by how many cells can you

221
00:13:43.652 --> 00:13:45.052
inject and form a tumor?

222
00:13:46.452 --> 00:13:46.712
If you

223
00:13:47.732 --> 00:13:49.692
remember the orthotopic injection, we

